#. type: Plain text
#: build/C/man7/signal.7:299
msgid ""
"Up to and including Linux 2.2, the default behavior for B<SIGSYS>, "
"B<SIGXCPU>, B<SIGXFSZ>, and (on architectures other than SPARC and MIPS)  "
